---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
<section class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-10 py-16 px-6 bg-surface rounded-xl shadow-md">

  <!-- Profile Photo -->
  <div class="flex-shrink-0">
    <img
      src="/images/me.jpg"
      alt="Portrait of Dávid Juhász"
      class="w-40 h-40 rounded-full object-cover shadow-md border-4 border-muted"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Text Content -->
  <div class="max-w-xl sm:text-left text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-4">
      Welcome to My Digital Space
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
      My name is Dávid Juhász and I'm a Compiler & Systems Engnieer. I specialize in building compilers, toolchains, and low-level runtime systems where hardware and software meet. My work spans LLVM-based code generation, embedded firmware, system simulation, and performance-tuned tooling for hardware accelerators.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
      This site is still early in its journey — I’ve recently decided to be more intentional about sharing my work and ideas publicly. While some sections may be light for now, I’ll be adding more over time, including technical deep-dives, project highlights, and insights on systems, developer tools, and software engineering.
    </p>
    <!-- p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
      This site is a space to share my work, insights, and engineering philosophy — from real-world projects to explorations in developer tooling and system design. I'll be expanding it with a blog in the near future.
    </p -->
    <p class="text-lg text-text mb-8">
      If any of this resonates — whether you're curious about my work, exploring collaboration, or just want to connect — feel free to reach out or explore more using the buttons below.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-start gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/juhaszdavid"
        data-goatcounter-click="linkedin-profile"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="bg-accent text-bg px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium shadow hover:bg-opacity-90 transition"
      >
        Connect on LinkedIn
      </a>
      <a
        href="/portfolio"
        class="border border-accent text-accent px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-accent hover:text-bg transition"
      >
        View Portfolio
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:Dávid%20Juhász<&#x68;&#x65;&#x6C;&#x6C;&#x6F;&#x40;&#x64;&#x61;&#x76;&#x69;&#x64;&#x6A;&#x75;&#x68;&#x61;&#x73;&#x7A;&#x2E;&#x64;&#x65;&#x76;>"
        class="border border-accent text-accent px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-accent hover:text-bg transition"
      >
        Email Me
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

</BaseLayout>
